1
00:00:01,100 --> 00:00:03,930
Hey, all you viewers out there!

2
00:00:03,930 --> 00:00:07,270
When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make sure to keep the room nice and bright,

3
00:00:07,270 --> 00:00:09,260
and sit back from the screen, 'kay?

4
00:00:10,840 --> 00:00:13,140
Previously on Fairy Tail!

5
00:00:13,140 --> 00:00:15,580
During the initial confrontations with Phantom Lord,

6
00:00:15,580 --> 00:00:17,780
Master and Erza were defeated!

7
00:00:17,780 --> 00:00:20,040
In order for us to stop the Magic Giant,

8
00:00:20,040 --> 00:00:22,700
we have to defeat the Element 4.

9
00:00:22,700 --> 00:00:25,210
And by the way, Lucy, who is being targeted by Phantom,

10
00:00:25,450 --> 00:00:27,800
was hidden away in the safe-house, but...

11
00:00:27,800 --> 00:00:28,960
I've got a bad feeling about this.

12
00:00:49,220 --> 00:00:53,630
It'll be all right! I'll yell it out countless times.

13
00:00:53,630 --> 00:00:58,700
I believe your every tomorrow will be shining.

14
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:01,050
The intersection of all people

15
00:01:01,050 --> 00:01:03,660
whose dreams have come true is one point:

16
00:01:03,660 --> 00:01:08,290
Never giving up.  And that's why we're not gonna lose!

17
00:01:08,290 --> 00:01:13,470
When it seems like you'll be blown away by the headwinds,

18
00:01:13,470 --> 00:01:15,620
grasp this hand, try to take a chance.

19
00:01:15,620 --> 00:01:18,890
Because you're not alone anymore, got it?

20
00:01:22,010 --> 00:01:24,000
Go forward, more and more!

21
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:26,520
Don't give up on your awesome dream!

22
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:27,780
That's right, don't cry!

23
00:01:27,780 --> 00:01:29,250
Move on, my way!

24
00:01:29,250 --> 00:01:31,630
Now, with the light shining down upon you.

25
00:01:31,630 --> 00:01:33,710
Don't even think about something like giving up!

26
00:01:33,710 --> 00:01:36,140
Even if you trade being hurt again for strength.

27
00:01:36,140 --> 00:01:41,630
Your eyes, always looking straight ahead,

28
00:01:41,630 --> 00:01:45,910
can surely see the light!

29
00:02:08,920 --> 00:02:10,820
Wow, you're right!

30
00:02:10,820 --> 00:02:14,230
The Magic Giant's writing speed has slowed down considerably, right?

31
00:02:14,230 --> 00:02:15,870
So that's it.

32
00:02:15,870 --> 00:02:18,970
Fire, water, wind, and earth.

33
00:02:18,970 --> 00:02:23,280
A Magic Giant that moves using the power of the four elements.

34
00:02:23,810 --> 00:02:27,620
And the source of that magical power is the Element 4.

35
00:02:28,060 --> 00:02:31,630
Totomaru of the Conflagration, who was guarding Jupiter.

36
00:02:31,630 --> 00:02:34,340
Sol of the Land, who Elfman defeated.

37
00:02:34,610 --> 00:02:39,090
And there's Juvia of the Deep, who Gray defeated.

38
00:02:39,090 --> 00:02:41,130
Then that means there's only one left.

39
00:02:41,130 --> 00:02:44,330
If we can defeat that fourth member, we can stop the giant.

40
00:02:44,330 --> 00:02:47,570
Which means we can stop them from casting Abyss Break.

41
00:02:47,570 --> 00:02:51,230
The final one, Aria of the Heavens.

42
00:02:51,230 --> 00:02:54,500
The strongest wizard of the Element 4.

43
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:59,680
And he's the one who took the master's magical power! He's a fearsome opponent.

44
00:03:07,910 --> 00:03:09,400
My imagination?

45
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:15,120
Wings of Flame!

46
00:03:21,850 --> 00:03:25,260
You hold up quite well, Salamander.

47
00:03:25,620 --> 00:03:28,510
I'm all fired up, you bastard!

48
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:29,890
Natsu...

49
00:03:30,190 --> 00:03:32,100
Airspace... Suppress!

50
00:03:37,430 --> 00:03:39,070
He's too strong!

51
00:03:39,070 --> 00:03:42,610
So this is the strongest man in the Element 4!

52
00:03:42,610 --> 00:03:43,960
Damn it...

53
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:47,200
There's always someone better, young dragon...

54
00:03:47,500 --> 00:03:49,370
Then how about this?

55
00:03:49,370 --> 00:03:51,830
Roar of the Fire Dragon!

56
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,720
He disappeared!

57
00:03:56,060 --> 00:03:57,340
Where'd he go?

58
00:03:58,170 --> 00:04:00,170
This is over, Salamander.

59
00:04:00,430 --> 00:04:04,860
Let me give you the same suffering I gave to Makarov...

60
00:04:06,870 --> 00:04:09,100
Airspace... Ruin!

61
00:04:11,100 --> 00:04:12,670
The sadness!

62
00:04:12,670 --> 00:04:18,400
No matter the wizard, inside this airspace their magical power will empty!

63
00:04:21,670 --> 00:04:22,860
My power...

64
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,850
...it's being sucked out...

65
00:04:24,850 --> 00:04:26,320
Natsu!

66
00:04:29,950 --> 00:04:32,290
Damn it all...

67
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:37,560
Erza!

68
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:40,880
Hey, is it okay for you to move with that injury?

69
00:04:44,260 --> 00:04:46,210
Erza's angry!

70
00:04:46,210 --> 00:04:48,020
He's the one who did that to the master?

71
00:04:48,020 --> 00:04:49,760
Erza Scarlet?

72
00:04:50,060 --> 00:04:51,500
How sad.

73
00:04:51,500 --> 00:04:56,350
For me to have the head of not only Salamander, but Titania as well!

74
00:04:56,590 --> 00:05:00,150
So you're the bastard who laid hands on him. He's like a father to us!

75
00:05:00,450 --> 00:05:01,490
Erza!

76
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:06,420
Since I get to actually face Erza...

77
00:05:06,420 --> 00:05:09,910
...then I suppose I have no choice but to fight seriously!

78
00:05:11,950 --> 00:05:13,030
His eyes?

79
00:05:13,030 --> 00:05:13,950
Yes.

80
00:05:13,950 --> 00:05:15,500
What about his eyeballs?

81
00:05:15,790 --> 00:05:18,310
Aria usually has his eyes closed.

82
00:05:18,310 --> 00:05:23,070
By closing his eyes he suppresses the overwhelming magical power he possesses, it seems.

83
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:24,630
What?

84
00:05:24,930 --> 00:05:29,530
Anyway, if you find Aria, beat him before he can open his eyes!

85
00:05:29,530 --> 00:05:33,260
If he opens them, you might lose any chance at victory.

86
00:05:35,710 --> 00:05:36,650
What's that?

87
00:05:36,650 --> 00:05:38,190
The magic circle is glowing!

88
00:05:38,190 --> 00:05:39,400
Is it complete?

89
00:05:40,250 --> 00:05:43,360
Damn it... Is this as far as we go?

90
00:05:46,900 --> 00:05:49,200
Natsu... Everyone...

91
00:05:49,450 --> 00:05:50,570
I'm counting on you!

92
00:05:58,790 --> 00:06:01,210
Come, Titania!

93
00:06:03,170 --> 00:06:06,220
Activate the Airspace of Death, Zero!

94
00:06:06,220 --> 00:06:09,430
This Airspace will consume all life within it!

95
00:06:12,450 --> 00:06:14,940
This isn't good at all!

96
00:06:14,940 --> 00:06:17,310
Magic that consumes life?

97
00:06:18,260 --> 00:06:23,820
How? How can you take people's lives so easily?

98
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,360
You villain!

99
00:06:25,660 --> 00:06:28,300
Now, let's enjoy this!

100
00:06:28,300 --> 00:06:29,570
Erza!

101
00:06:30,610 --> 00:06:33,910
Can you withstand this Airspace?

102
00:06:40,330 --> 00:06:41,420
Impossible!

103
00:06:41,420 --> 00:06:43,770
She's slicing through the Airspace?!

104
00:06:46,590 --> 00:06:47,920
Heaven's Wheel!

105
00:06:50,590 --> 00:06:52,690
Blumenblatt!

106
00:06:58,910 --> 00:07:00,710
She beat him in one hit!

107
00:07:00,710 --> 00:07:02,600
Erza's dangerous, that's for sure!

108
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:06,380
The likes of you should never have been able to beat the master.

109
00:07:07,370 --> 00:07:11,450
Your days of glory will be wiped out, starting now.

110
00:07:11,450 --> 00:07:14,120
T-The sadness...

111
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:15,630
Can we block it?

112
00:07:15,630 --> 00:07:17,920
It's not something blockable!

113
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,730
What should we do?

114
00:07:23,470 --> 00:07:24,730
What?

115
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,360
The light's disappeared!

116
00:07:44,380 --> 00:07:45,840
Erza!

117
00:07:45,840 --> 00:07:47,310
Hey!

118
00:07:47,310 --> 00:07:48,570
What's this?

119
00:07:48,570 --> 00:07:50,440
Is this Natsu's doing?

120
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:52,390
It's stopped!

121
00:07:52,390 --> 00:07:54,700
Abyss Break has been terminated!

122
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,200
Seriously?

123
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:57,830
Which means...

124
00:07:57,830 --> 00:08:00,650
The power of the four elements has been cut off.

125
00:08:01,530 --> 00:08:02,830
They did it!

126
00:08:02,830 --> 00:08:05,340
The giant has been stopped!

127
00:08:07,110 --> 00:08:09,560
The Element 4 are defeated?

128
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:11,130
I knew they could do it.

129
00:08:14,910 --> 00:08:16,850
Reedus, are you okay?

130
00:08:16,850 --> 00:08:17,480
Oui...

131
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:19,480
Quite the stubborn one.

132
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:23,900
Hey there, Double Stuf, it's about time you gave up and handed that girl over.

133
00:08:23,900 --> 00:08:26,310
Our master is waiting, you see.

134
00:08:27,990 --> 00:08:30,130
Lucy, hurry up and run.

135
00:08:30,130 --> 00:08:32,680
What are you saying? I'll fight too!

136
00:08:32,680 --> 00:08:34,820
It's for everyone's sake!

137
00:08:34,820 --> 00:08:35,750
Please!

138
00:08:35,750 --> 00:08:36,360
But...

139
00:08:36,660 --> 00:08:38,480
Oh, you're makin' me cry.

140
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,880
How touching.

141
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:41,410
I like it.

142
00:08:41,670 --> 00:08:42,830
Pict Magic!

143
00:08:43,790 --> 00:08:45,750
Roar of Silver!

144
00:08:45,950 --> 00:08:49,250
Oh, it's Vulcans! I've seen them on Mt. Hakobe.

145
00:08:49,250 --> 00:08:50,400
Mirror Magic!

146
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:52,380
Form Mirror!

147
00:08:55,310 --> 00:08:59,220
Any hostility is reflected by these mirrors.

148
00:08:59,220 --> 00:09:00,570
See ya!

149
00:09:01,650 --> 00:09:03,430
Reedus!

150
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:04,560
I'm sorry!

151
00:09:06,570 --> 00:09:10,830
Leaving your ally and running away, Princess?

152
00:09:10,830 --> 00:09:13,740
You Fairy Butts ain't so hot after all.

153
00:09:13,740 --> 00:09:15,820
If they'd let somebody like you join!

154
00:09:15,820 --> 00:09:16,890
Why, you...

155
00:09:16,890 --> 00:09:18,070
You wanna go?

156
00:09:18,370 --> 00:09:19,490
Sound Attack!

157
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:21,460
Howling!

158
00:09:25,660 --> 00:09:26,580
Reedus!

159
00:09:26,860 --> 00:09:32,120
How weak... You actually like hanging out with these guys, Princess?

160
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:34,530
Why, you... You...

161
00:09:35,550 --> 00:09:37,470
You'll never...

162
00:09:43,140 --> 00:09:46,880
What's going on? Did they stop the giant?

163
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:54,300
Now that's what I call a greeting!

164
00:09:54,300 --> 00:09:56,360
What have you done to Lucy?

165
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:58,810
Return the girl at once.

166
00:09:59,180 --> 00:10:00,650
Or else...

167
00:10:01,230 --> 00:10:04,040
I'll erase you from this world!

168
00:10:04,230 --> 00:10:08,090
Perfect. I've been looking to have some fun.

169
00:10:08,090 --> 00:10:09,870
I'll take you on!

170
00:10:17,350 --> 00:10:18,010
Loke...

171
00:10:18,610 --> 00:10:22,720
What's with the strange vibes I'm getting from him?

172
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:25,670
He's not just some Holder-type wizard, is he?

173
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:28,660
Who the hell are you?

174
00:10:28,660 --> 00:10:30,660
You smell weird.

175
00:10:30,660 --> 00:10:31,900
Don't smell me.

176
00:10:32,250 --> 00:10:34,660
I'd rather not be sniffed by guys.

177
00:10:36,280 --> 00:10:37,650
Not now!

178
00:10:41,270 --> 00:10:43,070
My imagination?

179
00:10:43,070 --> 00:10:44,950
He was totally weak!

180
00:10:45,250 --> 00:10:47,520
Bozu, Sue, I'm heading back.

181
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:49,570
Clean up that lady-killer there.

182
00:10:49,570 --> 00:10:50,820
Roger that...

183
00:10:50,820 --> 00:10:51,870
I won't let you...

184
00:10:52,130 --> 00:10:53,250
Sound Attack!

185
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:55,090
Disturbed!

186
00:11:00,590 --> 00:11:02,430
Mirror Magic!

187
00:11:03,630 --> 00:11:05,010
Kaleidoscope!

188
00:11:06,580 --> 00:11:09,330
It's impossible for you to escape from there for a while.

189
00:11:09,330 --> 00:11:12,170
Have a good look at your own pitiful form.

190
00:11:16,620 --> 00:11:18,630
Unbelievable.

191
00:11:18,630 --> 00:11:24,700
Those Element 4 were wiped out fighting that worthless Fairy Tail?

192
00:11:24,700 --> 00:11:27,850
If you're beat by trash, then you're trash yourself.

193
00:11:27,850 --> 00:11:31,200
Oh, you've returned, Gajeel?

194
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:33,370
I've brought a present, Master.

195
00:11:36,310 --> 00:11:38,440
That was quick.

196
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:42,070
But you did an excellent job finding her, Gajeel.

197
00:11:42,070 --> 00:11:45,930
Don't underestimate the nose of a Dragon Slayer.

198
00:11:46,150 --> 00:11:48,140
You're sure she's still alive?

199
00:11:48,140 --> 00:11:50,520
This is all pointless if she isn't.

200
00:11:51,710 --> 00:11:54,080
I did rough her up a lot.

201
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:55,730
See?

202
00:12:01,820 --> 00:12:03,780
Looks like she's still kickin'!

203
00:12:03,780 --> 00:12:08,160
Now that's my guild. Only the strongest wizards.

204
00:12:11,810 --> 00:12:14,560
Attention all you from Fairy Tail.

205
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:17,400
Please listen carefully to this voice.

206
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:18,260
What's this?

207
00:12:18,260 --> 00:12:19,460
It's Master Jose!

208
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:22,460
That voice!

209
00:12:22,460 --> 00:12:23,820
It's Lucy!

210
00:12:23,820 --> 00:12:24,970
Oh, no!

211
00:12:24,970 --> 00:12:28,500
We have captured Lucy.

212
00:12:28,500 --> 00:12:32,850
So, we have accomplished one of our objectives.

213
00:12:33,150 --> 00:12:37,900
Thus we have one final goal that remains to be fulfilled.

214
00:12:38,580 --> 00:12:41,540
Wiping you off the face of this earth!

215
00:12:41,540 --> 00:12:43,670
You worthless brats!

216
00:12:43,670 --> 00:12:45,430
Damn him!

217
00:12:56,560 --> 00:13:02,640
I'm sorry, Lucy... I wasn't able to protect you...

218
00:13:02,640 --> 00:13:03,870
I'm sorry...

219
00:13:04,870 --> 00:13:06,110
I'm sorry...

220
00:13:09,990 --> 00:13:12,440
I knew something bad would happen...

221
00:13:13,250 --> 00:13:14,740
And yet...

222
00:13:15,040 --> 00:13:17,090
Why didn't I come earlier?

223
00:13:18,530 --> 00:13:21,680
No... I was scared...

224
00:13:23,030 --> 00:13:26,810
Lucy, scared to be close to you!

225
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:32,740
I'm the worst!

226
00:13:34,510 --> 00:13:38,730
Seriously... I really do look pitiful.

227
00:13:41,150 --> 00:13:43,960
Isn't that right, Karen?

228
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:52,920
What is it now?

229
00:13:52,920 --> 00:13:56,520
I think the number of Shades has increased!

230
00:13:58,190 --> 00:14:01,440
Give us a break here... They're still at it?

231
00:14:08,250 --> 00:14:10,740
Watch over Lucy.

232
00:14:11,790 --> 00:14:15,790
There are a number of bugs still in my guild building.

233
00:14:15,790 --> 00:14:17,520
Salamander, too?

234
00:14:17,520 --> 00:14:18,820
Yes.

235
00:14:19,260 --> 00:14:21,210
However...

236
00:14:21,210 --> 00:14:25,550
I'll show them there won't be any more miracles...

237
00:14:26,280 --> 00:14:29,600
I'll clean them up myself!

238
00:14:30,430 --> 00:14:33,390
Damn it! Lucy's been...

239
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:38,480
Natsu...

240
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:39,480
Erza!

241
00:14:40,650 --> 00:14:41,960
Unleash...

242
00:14:44,450 --> 00:14:45,770
...your power!

243
00:14:47,950 --> 00:14:54,370
You have... power... sleeping within you...

244
00:14:54,910 --> 00:14:57,020
Believe in yourself...

245
00:14:57,680 --> 00:14:59,260
Break though...

246
00:15:00,070 --> 00:15:01,710
And call it forth!

247
00:15:03,100 --> 00:15:05,080
Now is the time...

248
00:15:06,310 --> 00:15:07,750
Protect Lucy...

249
00:15:08,380 --> 00:15:10,670
Protect the guild!

250
00:15:11,730 --> 00:15:13,980
Go, Natsu!

251
00:15:13,980 --> 00:15:18,220
You're the one who will surpass me!

252
00:15:42,030 --> 00:15:43,370
Natsu, huh?

253
00:15:45,010 --> 00:15:46,340
Makarov...

254
00:15:47,670 --> 00:15:49,350
How do you feel?

255
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:53,460
You should stay in bed.

256
00:15:55,450 --> 00:15:58,070
And you think I'll listen to you?

257
00:15:59,210 --> 00:16:04,350
Considering your age, don't you think it's a bit early for you to have recovered?

258
00:16:04,350 --> 00:16:08,270
The "age" crack wasn't necessary.

259
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:12,240
You going to your death?

260
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:15,700
I'm going to do my duty as a parent. That's all.

261
00:16:20,190 --> 00:16:22,200
Sorry for the trouble.

262
00:16:28,760 --> 00:16:30,130
Honestly...

263
00:16:30,770 --> 00:16:32,590
You never change.

264
00:16:36,910 --> 00:16:38,270
Erza!

265
00:16:39,030 --> 00:16:40,270
Erza!

266
00:16:40,270 --> 00:16:42,890
Looks like there were some fireworks here too.

267
00:16:42,890 --> 00:16:44,270
It's you guys.

268
00:16:44,270 --> 00:16:46,330
When did you break in?

269
00:16:46,330 --> 00:16:48,080
You shouldn't even be standing!

270
00:16:48,080 --> 00:16:49,740
H-Hey!

271
00:16:51,440 --> 00:16:52,860
Aria?

272
00:16:52,860 --> 00:16:55,750
You actually fought with wounds like that?

273
00:16:55,750 --> 00:16:57,550
What were you thinking?

274
00:16:57,550 --> 00:16:58,580
Which means...

275
00:16:58,580 --> 00:17:00,080
You defeated Aria?

276
00:17:00,380 --> 00:17:04,860
I never wanted you to see me so weak like this...

277
00:17:05,190 --> 00:17:07,460
I guess I still have a long way to go.

278
00:17:09,390 --> 00:17:10,090
What's that?

279
00:17:11,750 --> 00:17:13,050
That's...

280
00:17:13,050 --> 00:17:14,850
I sense death!

281
00:17:15,580 --> 00:17:17,870
What is this feeling?

282
00:17:18,750 --> 00:17:20,980
It sends chills down a Man's spine!

283
00:17:20,980 --> 00:17:23,010
The malice is palpable!

284
00:17:26,330 --> 00:17:32,690
My, my. I'm quite impressed, my Fairy Tail Wizards...

285
00:17:33,610 --> 00:17:39,450
To think I would be able to have such fun... I never would have dreamed it.

286
00:17:40,170 --> 00:17:45,200
Destroying Jupiter, taking down the Element 4...

287
00:17:45,490 --> 00:17:49,500
And even bringing my Magic Giant to its knees!

288
00:17:49,760 --> 00:17:50,920
Master Jose!

289
00:17:50,920 --> 00:17:52,080
This guy's...

290
00:17:52,080 --> 00:17:53,300
...Phantom's master?

291
00:17:53,620 --> 00:17:56,020
What incredible evil magical power!

292
00:17:56,020 --> 00:17:58,630
I feel nauseous just standing near him!

293
00:17:58,930 --> 00:18:03,850
Now, I must thank you for the fun you've given me.

294
00:18:03,850 --> 00:18:04,660
Elfman!

295
00:18:04,660 --> 00:18:05,470
Right!

296
00:18:05,790 --> 00:18:08,260
I'll enjoy this...

297
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:12,800
Ice Make...

298
00:18:12,800 --> 00:18:14,570
Beast Arm!

299
00:18:14,570 --> 00:18:16,620
Wait, don't be hasty!

300
00:18:16,620 --> 00:18:18,490
Saucer!

301
00:18:16,620 --> 00:18:18,490
Iron Bull!

302
00:18:18,490 --> 00:18:19,980
Absurd!

303
00:18:24,750 --> 00:18:27,120
Elfman, Gray!

304
00:18:56,280 --> 00:19:00,490
You. I'm pretty sure you took a direct hit from Jupiter.

305
00:19:01,100 --> 00:19:03,230
How is it you can stand?

306
00:19:03,230 --> 00:19:07,550
My friends strengthen my heart!

307
00:19:08,820 --> 00:19:11,670
For those that I love...

308
00:19:11,670 --> 00:19:13,710
...I'd throw away this body!

309
00:19:14,030 --> 00:19:17,790
Strong, courageous, beautiful...

310
00:19:17,790 --> 00:19:21,680
It will be such a pleasure to destroy you, girl!

311
00:19:26,160 --> 00:19:27,850
Not too bad a sound.

312
00:19:30,850 --> 00:19:33,770
But man, what a lame reaction...

313
00:19:34,070 --> 00:19:37,120
Gajeel, don't you think you should stop now?

314
00:19:37,120 --> 00:19:39,970
You keep doing this, and it'll be serious trouble!

315
00:19:40,780 --> 00:19:42,740
But I'm bored.

316
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:45,740
The master sure is cruel.

317
00:19:45,740 --> 00:19:48,480
Making me watch over the girl like this,

318
00:19:48,480 --> 00:19:51,410
and going to deal with the flies himself.

319
00:19:52,460 --> 00:19:56,080
What's the harm in doing this to pass the time, huh?

320
00:19:56,080 --> 00:20:01,170
Stop it. If the master finds out, he won't let you off so easy!

321
00:20:02,210 --> 00:20:03,590
Shut up.

322
00:20:03,590 --> 00:20:08,730
Maybe she's some noblewoman or something, but to me she's nothing but Fairy Butt trash.

323
00:20:08,730 --> 00:20:12,140
And even if she's a woman, she's still a Wizard.

324
00:20:12,570 --> 00:20:15,770
She should be prepared for this when she joined a guild.

325
00:20:16,070 --> 00:20:17,960
But you're going overboard.

326
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:19,110
What a waste...

327
00:20:19,110 --> 00:20:21,570
Master's gonna be pissed, big time.

328
00:20:21,910 --> 00:20:24,700
If that happens, I'll blame it on you guys.

329
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:26,980
What a jerk...

330
00:20:26,980 --> 00:20:29,150
But man, how stupid.

331
00:20:29,150 --> 00:20:33,680
Now that they know she's rich, the Fairy Butts are frantic to get her back.

332
00:20:35,840 --> 00:20:39,310
You guys really are complete idiots.

333
00:20:39,690 --> 00:20:43,260
So pitiful... I think I'm tearing up.

334
00:20:44,610 --> 00:20:46,670
What is she thinking?

335
00:20:46,670 --> 00:20:48,470
She's provoking Gajeel.

336
00:20:48,770 --> 00:20:52,420
Phantom Lord? The rulers of spirits?

337
00:20:52,420 --> 00:20:55,230
What a joke! I'm not scared of you at all!

338
00:20:55,230 --> 00:20:56,980
Oh, I see then.

339
00:20:59,390 --> 00:21:04,070
You've got some balls bluffing in a situation like this.

340
00:21:04,070 --> 00:21:07,040
I must say that's not bad...

341
00:21:08,100 --> 00:21:12,140
But, you see... What I want to hear isn't your backtalk.

342
00:21:12,140 --> 00:21:13,630
I want to hear you scream.

343
00:21:13,630 --> 00:21:16,830
You don't start yelling and there's going to be trouble.

344
00:21:16,830 --> 00:21:20,620
Then why don't you try killing me?

345
00:21:20,620 --> 00:21:25,710
You do that, and you'll be in bigger trouble.

346
00:21:26,670 --> 00:21:28,420
Well, that sounds interesting.

347
00:21:28,420 --> 00:21:29,550
Let me hear it.

348
00:21:30,150 --> 00:21:34,200
Fairy Tail would never forgive you.

349
00:21:34,200 --> 00:21:36,380
That's the kind of guild they are!

350
00:21:37,620 --> 00:21:44,480
You'd be shivering under the shadow of the world's scariest guild every day...

351
00:21:44,480 --> 00:21:45,820
For the rest of your lives!

352
00:21:46,120 --> 00:21:48,490
That sounds like fun, too.

353
00:21:48,490 --> 00:21:50,940
Let's try that out!

354
00:21:51,660 --> 00:21:52,540
Gajeel!

355
00:21:52,540 --> 00:21:53,430
Stop it!

356
00:22:09,930 --> 00:22:11,430
I knew it.

357
00:22:11,650 --> 00:22:14,010
I noticed your smell!

358
00:22:14,010 --> 00:22:15,950
Salamander!

359
00:22:15,950 --> 00:22:18,460
Gajeel!

360
00:23:56,160 --> 00:24:00,070
The Iron Dragon Slayer... So that means he eats iron, right?

361
00:24:00,070 --> 00:24:01,290
Probably.

362
00:24:01,290 --> 00:24:05,990
Just like you eat fire, Natsu, he should eat his element.

363
00:24:05,990 --> 00:24:10,060
Then couldn't you become the Fish Dragon Slayer, Happy?

364
00:24:10,060 --> 00:24:12,120
Fish Dragon?

365
00:24:12,120 --> 00:24:14,250
That might be kinda cool!

366
00:24:14,250 --> 00:24:17,110
Next time: The Two Dragon Slayers!

367
00:24:17,110 --> 00:24:20,180
What would the Roar of the Fish Dragon be like?

368
00:24:20,180 --> 00:24:22,640
You'd shoot fish or something from your mouth...

369
00:24:22,640 --> 00:24:24,600
That's not really <i>me</i>...

370
00:24:24,600 --> 00:24:26,900


